            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="footer-content">
                <div class="footer-section">
                    <h3>About Medicare</h3>
                    <p>Leading healthcare provider focused on providing exceptional medical services with a commitment to patient care and innovative treatment solutions.</p>
                    <div class="footer-links">
                        <a href="#"><i class="fas fa-angle-right"></i> About Us</a>
